Detailed Description

cvmx_bgx::_cmr::_rx_stat4

These registers provide a count of all packets received that were dropped by the DMAC filter. Packets that match the DMAC are dropped and counted here regardless of whether they were ERR packets, but does not include those reported in BGX()_CMR()_RX_STAT6. These packets are never counted in BGX()_CMR()_RX_STAT0. Eight-byte packets as the result of truncation or other means are not dropped by CNXXXX and will never appear in this count.
